name: Steins;Gate VN Original Art + Huke Artstyle
description:
This model is able to do most of main characters of Steins;Gate in the iconic style of Steins;Gate visual novels as well as background in this style.

To generate characters in style of steins gate use styhuke, sgnovelcg, sgzeronovelcg words. I also recommend using no humans in negative tags, unless you want steins;gate VN like background, then use it in positive tags.

The model is also is able to replicate general huke artstyle (use styhuke), general steins;gate novel artstyle (sgnovelcg), black rock shooter artstyle and knows some characters that base model wasn't able to generate.

Trained on top of strawberry-mix which is Anything-v3 based, so using some VAE is absolutely required.

Strongly reccomend "text" in negative tags.

Example prompts and settings are in model examples.
